 EXPLANATIONS: There 2 Moons in Ultima IV.
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~ The teleportation zone teleports you depending on the moon
               position and the place from where (which town) you are
               teleported.Teleportation doors appear near all the towns.
               For example:to go to the Shrine Of Spiritualty,you have
               to take the teleporation from MINOC (Search for the door
               east of MINOC) and wait until the 2 moons draw this:
                 /\  /\
                <  ><  > to be teleported to the Shrine...
                 \/  \/
