 SEQUENCE OF THE STONES TO GET THE 3-PART KEYS :
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 To get each part of the key,you have to get the stones which lies in the
 dungeons,except the white stone (look the coordinates in the Items list),
 which lies north-west of the Castle of lord british.To get it,take
 the balloon after the dungeon HYTHLOTH accessible from the castle of
 Lord bristish.
 The black stone lies in the country too.It lies on the square of a tele-
 portation door near MOONGLOW.To get the Black Stone,just wait untill the
 2 Moons are dark and type: (s)earch on the square...
 The 3-part key can be built only with your eight stones in altar rooms,
 in dungeons.The key is in three part:

  (T)ruth= GREEN + PURPLE + BLUE + WHITE   Stones
(C)ourage= ORANGE + RED + PURPLE + WHITE   Stones
   (L)ove= ORANGE + YELLOW + GREEN + WHITE Stones

  C L :SACRIFICE IS ORANGE  found in:COVETOUS magic wheel for S D I level 7
    L :COMPASSION IS YELLOW         :DESPISE              for   D   level 5
T   L :JUSTICE IS GREEN             :WRONG                for   D I level 8
  C   :VALOR IS RED                 :DESTARD              for S     level 7
T C   :HONOR IS PURPLE              :SHAME                for S   I level 2
T     :HONESTY IS BLUE              :DECEIT               for     I level 7
T C L :SPIRITUALTY IS WHITE         :HYTHLOTH             for S D I level 1
                                                              | | |
